  "notes": "Sarasota FL Clerk — custom in-house ClerkNet ASP.NET WebForms + Telerik app at secure.sarasotaclerk.com/OfficialRecords.aspx (probed 2026-06-10, Wave-1 BRUNO). NO Cloudflare, NO CAPTCHA, NO disclaimer gate. Single-page WebForms flow: GET OfficialRecords.aspx -> scrape __VIEWSTATE/__VIEWSTATEGENERATOR/__EVENTVALIDATION -> POST same URL with tbParty (last-first-no-comma), rdAppFrom/rdAppTo dateInput, optional cbDocType$N checkboxes (post name=value-code), bSearch_input=Search. Results render into Telerik RadGrid ctl00_cphBody_rgCaseList on the same page (rgRow/rgAltRow rows). 277 doc-type codes captured 2026-06-10 (DEED='D' single type, no WD/QCD split; NOC='NC'). Direct retrieval by Instrument # via tbLic field; Book/Page via tbBook/tbPage. UNVERIFIED pending first operator-approved live POST (Wave 2): result-grid column order, paging, per-row doc-image href pattern. Adapter at adapters/sarasota_clerknet_http_adapter.py parses grid header text -> column map at runtime so column-order changes are tolerated. Re-scrape hidden WebForms fields from every response before the next POST. Probe notes: src/titlepro/api/downloaded_doc/0610/Sarasota_BRUNO_v1/phase0_probe_recorder.md."
